{"tid":169664,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無對屋企人講過好mean既說話","createTime":"2017-03-24T10:18:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T10:31:15.000Z","uid":93534,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8336d1ba503d3d2c83a5cd8a5e192085030c8f3c","tid":169664,"uid":93534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T10:18:34.000Z","msg":"記得中學既時候 爸媽返晏既話<br />\n是旦一個都會提早起身整早餐比我食<br />\n但我懶訓 成日預到d時間猛猛緊<br />\n份早餐一係無時間食一係食唔哂就趕住出門<br />\n之後有次媽咪講左句<br />\n「成日煮完又唔食 早d起身呀嘛」<br />\n個陣就遲到 炆炆地 回左句<br />\n「你日日都整呢d 又唔好食」<br />\n就出左門口<br />\n講完個一刻其實好內疚 覺得自己好唔顧佢地感受<br />\n佢地係特登早起身煮比我<br />\n煮完訓一陣又要返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比著我個女/仔咁同我講野 一定好傷心<br />\n<br />\n人大左 雖然覺得佢地有時都仲係好煩<br />\n但係仲有得比佢煩住 係幸福既煩 好想一世都比佢地煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：媽咪煮野真心唔好食"},{"pid":"9c42f3abce47b6fcca92609faa4a1723d0fdbace","tid":169664,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T10:20:38.000Z","msg":"佢地重要若無其事繼續對你好"},{"pid":"bde16a2463e5f412dba275807206a2b2593b203b","tid":169664,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T10:21:44.000Z","msg":"佢地講野賤過我好多"},{"pid":"e98150509f3bcd7a189a8e4abb926196fcefda14","tid":169664,"uid":76399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T10:22:01.000Z","msg":"點解同學晚晚都有好嘢食，我只係得魚蛋紫菜湯?"},{"pid":"934fe059c1079a841eced0e2db4494a79590b6af","tid":169664,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T10:23:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解同學晚晚都有好嘢食，我只係得魚蛋紫菜湯?</blockquote><br />\n鬼都識上網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38e57f4903190b903d2252a2e8872f7d56092ea3","tid":169664,"uid":76171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-2